---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Refund Policy"
  description="Pixel8 Multimedia refund and returns policy for made-to-order wall art."
>
  <section class="relative bg-bg-secondary py-16">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-pop-orange"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 font-dm text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-pop-orange transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-off-white">Refund Policy</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-5xl text-off-white tracking-wide mb-4" style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">REFUND POLICY</h1>
      <p class="font-dm text-gray-400 text-sm">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-8 font-dm text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Made to Order</h2>
        <p>All Pixel8 Multimedia products are made to order specifically for you. Because of this, we are unable to accept returns or offer refunds for change of mind. Please check your order carefully before completing your purchase.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Damaged or Faulty Items</h2>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged or with a printing defect, please contact us within 48 hours of delivery with photographs of the damage. We will arrange a free replacement at no extra cost to you. Please do not return the item without contacting us first.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Personalised Orders</h2>
        <p>Personalised items cannot be returned or refunded unless they arrive with a manufacturing or printing defect. We provide a digital proof for all personalised orders and do not begin printing until you have approved the proof. Once approved, the order is final.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Proof Approval</h2>
        <p>For personalised orders, you will receive a digital proof within 24-48 hours. You may request up to two rounds of revisions. Once you approve the final proof, printing begins and the order cannot be cancelled or refunded.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Incorrect Orders</h2>
        <p>If we have made an error with your order (wrong size, format, or design), please contact us immediately. We will correct the issue and send a replacement free of charge.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">How to Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For any issues with your order, please <a href="/contact" class="text-pixel-cyan hover:text-pop-orange transition-colors">contact us</a> with your order details and photographs where applicable. We aim to respond within 24 hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
